title: x/tools/cmd/vet: undefined: parser.ParseExprFrom
body:
When trying to `go get -u golang.org/x/tools/cmd/vet`, I get the following error:

```
# golang.org/x/tools/go/types
go/types/eval.go:68: undefined: parser.ParseExprFrom
```

Apparently introduced by https://github.com/golang/tools/commit/d241a1448bb9a6aeab0697421853a3ab1fbf243c.
